{title:My Soul Is Hungry}
{key:F}



Chorus:

[F]My soul is [F/A]hungry

For the [Bb]presence of the [Gm7]Lord

I want a [C7]feast not just a taste

Of the [Bb]Spirit and the [F]Word

[F]Show me the [F/A]storehouse

Where the [Bb]blessings are [Gm7]stored

My soul is [C7]hungry

For the presense of the [F]Lord


